items.title: How to debug error in model / tf.data which works fine in eager mode, but gives an error in keras.fit
items.body:
I set a batch of data from tf.data into the model, and the output of the model into my loss function.

Everything works fine, but I still get an error at one of the operations.

How do I go about debugging this? The graph doesn't give specific information on why the code is giving an error.
